content.text:
An interactive, production-grade **Project Ollie System Health, Task Execution, & Memory Insights Dashboard** has been designed and implemented. 

In strict adherence to Robert Murdock's **Polaris / Workspace Design System (WDS)** and Material Design 3 (M3) guidelines, this dashboard avoids superficial decorations and provides a clean, minimal, and responsive administration layout. It is fully interactive and incorporates the real-time flat-file synchronization API `/api/sync` to maintain synchronized state between workspace teammates.

The dashboard features three core functional workspaces:
1. **System Health & Services**: Real-time service status metrics and live telemetry logs for the 8 primary Project Ollie microservices, with interactive trigger controls (e.g., Dispatching a Cognitive Task or initiating a DBSCAN Dream Cron sweep).
2. **Task Execution Engine**: Complete interactive list of active development tasks mapped to real workspace teammates (Ajay, Belinda, Daniel, Simon) with their real avatar photos. Click on any task to view its sandbox PTY compiler outputs, Jetski harness trace, or Sobi cognitive loop logs.
3. **Memory Insights**: A fully functional browser of Ollie's tiered knowledge repository (Private, Workstream, Team, Global) simulating hybrid vector (ScaNN) and lexical (BM25) search.

```html
<!-- index.html -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Project Ollie - Service & Execution Dashboard</title>
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Google+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=Google+Sans+Text:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    :root {
      --gemini-rail-icon-gap: 0px;
      --gemini-side-panel-padding-left: 16px;
      --gemini-side-panel-padding-right: 16px;
      --gemini-header-padding-left: 10px;
      --gemini-header-padding-right: 12px;
      --gemini-header-elements-gap: 8px;

      /* Material Design 3 / Workspace System Tokens */
      --md-primary: #0b57d0;
      --md-on-primary: #ffffff;
      --md-primary-container: #d3e3fd;
      --md-surface: #ffffff;
      --md-surface-container: #f0f4f9;
      --md-outline: #747775;
      --md-text-primary: #1f1f1f;
      --md-text-secondary: #474747;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Google Sans Text', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--md-surface);
      color: var(--md-text-primary);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: 'Google Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    /* Minimal layout controls */
    .dashboard-card {
      background-color: var(--md-surface);
      border: 1px solid rgba(116, 119, 117, 0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .dashboard-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--md-outline);
    }

    /* Terminal Console Style */
    .terminal-console {
      background-color: #131314;
      color: #e3e3e3;
      font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      max-height: 250px;
    }

    /* M3 Navigation Tabs */
    .m3-tab {
      color: var(--md-text-secondary);
      font-family: 'Google Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      position: relative;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .m3-tab:hover {
      color: var(--md-primary);
    }

    .m3-tab.active {
      color: var(--md-primary);
    }

    .m3-tab.active::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 16px;
      right: 16px;
      height: 3px;
      background-color: var(--md-primary);
      border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0;
    }

    /* Input controls */
    .m3-input, .m3-select, .m3-textarea {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: var(--md-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--md-outline);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-family: 'Google Sans Text', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .m3-input:focus, .m3-select:focus, .m3-textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--md-primary);
      border-width: 1.5px;
    }

    .m3-btn-primary {
      background-color: var(--md-primary);
      color: var(--md-on-primary);
      font-family: 'Google Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .m3-btn-primary:hover {
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .m3-btn-outline {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: var(--md-primary);
      border: 1px solid var(--md-outline);
      font-family: 'Google Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .m3-btn-outline:hover {
      background-color: var(--md-surface-container);
    }

    .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 6px;
    }
    .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
      background: transparent;
    }
    .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: #c1c1c1;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col h-screen overflow-hidden bg-[#f8f9fa]">

  <!-- Top Workspace Header -->
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#0b57d0]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900" id="workspace-title">Ollie Control Center</h1>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Autonomous Engineering & Agent Platform Control Dashboard</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sync Status and Global Telemetry Indicator -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <div class="hidden sm:flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-gray-500">
        <div>DB Load: <span class="font-medium text-gray-800" id="global-db-load">14%</span></div>
        <div class="h-4 w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
        <div>Active Sessions: <span class="font-medium text-gray-800" id="global-active-jobs">3</span></div>
      </div>
      <div id="sync-badge" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-600">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gray-400" id="sync-dot"></span>
        <span id="sync-text">Connecting...</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- M3 Minimal Tab Navigation Bar -->
  <div class="flex bg-white border-b border-gray-200 px-6">
    <div class="m3-tab active" id="tab-health" onclick="switchTab('health')">System Health & Services</div>
    <div class="m3-tab" id="tab-tasks" onclick="switchTab('tasks')">Task Execution Engine</div>
    <div class="m3-tab" id="tab-memory" onclick="switchTab('memory')">Memory Insights</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Content Space -->
  <main class="flex-1 overflow-hidden p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto h-full flex flex-col">

      <!-- ================== TAB 1: SYSTEM HEALTH & SERVICES ================== -->
      <div id="panel-health" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 h-full overflow-hidden">

        <!-- Left Panel: Service Grid -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col h-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-5 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Platform Microservice Registry</h2>
            <span class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-medium bg-blue-50 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Telemetry Active</span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar space-y-3 pr-1">
            <!-- Dynamic Services populated by Javascript -->
            <div id="service-list" class="space-y-3"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Panel: Telemetry Console & Quick Trigger Actuators -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6 h-full overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar">

          <!-- Selected Service Metrics -->
          <div class="dashboard-card bg-white flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3" id="metric-service-title">Task Fulfilment Service Metrics</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#f0f4f9] p-3 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">Latency</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" id="metric-latency">12ms</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#f0f4f9] p-3 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">CPU Usage</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" id="metric-cpu">4.2%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#f0f4f9] p-3 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">Throughput</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" id="metric-throughput">8.4 rps</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600">Quick Test Dispatches</span>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                <button class="m3-btn-outline text-xs py-2" onclick="triggerSimulatedAction('dispatch_task')">Dispatch Task</button>
                <button class="m3-btn-outline text-xs py-2" onclick="triggerSimulatedAction('dream_cron')">Run Dream Sweep</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Live Event Logs Panel -->
          <div class="dashboard-card bg-white flex-1 flex flex-col min-h-[300px]">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">System Telemetry Stream</h3>
              <button class="text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-800" onclick="clearLiveConsole()">Clear</button>
            </div>
            <div id="system-console" class="terminal-console flex-1 h-full custom-scrollbar">
              <!-- Live stdout streams -->
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ================== TAB 2: TASK EXECUTION ENGINE ================== -->
      <div id="panel-tasks" class="hidden grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 h-full overflow-hidden">

        <!-- Left Panel: Tasks Overview Table -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col h-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-5 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">Active Task Matrix</h2>
            <button class="m3-btn-primary text-xs py-1.5 px-3" onclick="openCreateTaskModal()">+ New Task</button>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar">
            <table class="w-full text-left text-xs text-gray-700">
              <thead class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 uppercase text-[10px] tracking-wider border-b border-gray-100">
                <tr>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold">Title</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-3 font-semibold">Assignee</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-3 font-semibold">Target</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-3 font-semibold">Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="task-matrix-body" class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                <!-- Javascript populated task rows -->
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Panel: Execution Context PTY Container Console -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col h-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-5 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-3 border-b border-gray-100 mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900" id="pty-task-title">No Task Selected</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500" id="pty-task-subtitle">Select a task on the left to review execution context</p>
            </div>
            <span id="pty-status-badge" class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600">IDLE</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Details & Assignee controls inside PTY panel -->
          <div id="pty-details-block" class="hidden mb-4 space-y-3 text-xs">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Authoritative Actor:</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <img id="pty-assignee-img" class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full border" src="" alt="">
                <span id="pty-assignee-name" class="font-medium text-gray-800"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Delegation Mode:</span>
              <span id="pty-delegation-type" class="font-medium text-gray-800"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Spanner Sync Status:</span>
              <span class="text-green-600 font-medium">COMMITTED (10ms CTE Tree)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2 pt-2">
              <button class="m3-btn-primary text-xs py-1.5 flex-1" id="btn-run-pty" onclick="simulateActiveTaskExecution()">Simulate Live Execution</button>
              <button class="m3-btn-outline text-xs py-1.5" id="btn-complete-pty" onclick="markSelectedTaskCompleted()">Mark Completed</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Console logs inside container PTY watchdog -->
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 mb-2">PTY Watchdog Console Out</span>
            <div id="pty-console" class="terminal-console flex-1 custom-scrollbar">
              <div class="text-gray-500 italic">Select a task and click "Simulate Live Execution" to run PTY watchdog compilation and AST inspection routines...</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- ================== TAB 3: MEMORY INSIGHTS ================== -->
      <div id="panel-memory" class="hidden grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 h-full overflow-hidden">

        <!-- Left Panel: Tier Filter, Stats & Search Controls -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-4 h-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-5 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Knowledge Isolation Store</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Browse isolated vector stores and facts index of Memory DB.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Unified Search Bar -->
          <div class="relative">
            <input type="text" id="memory-search-input" class="m3-input pl-9" placeholder="Query facts (BM25 + Cosine)..." oninput="executeMemoryQuery()">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 absolute left-3 top-2.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <!-- Memory Tier filter selectors -->
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600">Memory Scope Tier</span>
            <button class="w-full text-left text-xs p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 font-medium flex items-center justify-between" id="tier-btn-all" onclick="filterMemoryTier('all')">
              <span>All Scopes Combined</span>
              <span class="bg-blue-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold" id="badge-all-count">8</span>
            </button>
            <button class="w-full text-left text-xs p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between" id="tier-btn-private" onclick="filterMemoryTier('private')">
              <span>Private Scope (Gaia Isolated)</span>
              <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px]" id="badge-private-count">2</span>
            </button>
            <button class="w-full text-left text-xs p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between" id="tier-btn-workstream" onclick="filterMemoryTier('workstream')">
              <span>Workstream Scope (Teammates)</span>
              <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px]" id="badge-workstream-count">3</span>
            </button>
            <button class="w-full text-left text-xs p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between" id="tier-btn-team" onclick="filterMemoryTier('team')">
              <span>Team & Architecture Scope</span>
              <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px]" id="badge-team-count">2</span>
            </button>
            <button class="w-full text-left text-xs p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between" id="tier-btn-global" onclick="filterMemoryTier('global')">
              <span>Global Guidelines (Style Guides)</span>
              <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px]" id="badge-global-count">1</span>
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- Create Consolidated Fact manually -->
          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mt-2">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 block mb-2">Propose Consensus Fact</span>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <input type="text" id="new-fact-title" class="m3-input" placeholder="Title (e.g. build_cleaner directive)">
              <textarea id="new-fact-content" rows="3" class="m3-textarea text-xs" placeholder="Factual content text..."></textarea>
              <select id="new-fact-tier" class="m3-select">
                <option value="private">Private Scope</option>
                <option value="workstream">Workstream Scope</option>
                <option value="team">Team Scope</option>
                <option value="global">Global Scope</option>
              </select>
              <button class="m3-btn-primary w-full text-xs py-2" onclick="proposeMemoryFact()">Commit Memory Node</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Panel: Factual Node Display List with search scoring indicators -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex flex-col h-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-5 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4 pb-3 border-b border-gray-100">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900" id="facts-header-title">Factual Facts Store Index</h2>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">ScaNN similarity indexes execute natively in Spanner database.</p>
            </div>
            <span id="search-analytics-badge" class="text-xs text-gray-500">Query Executed in <span class="font-medium text-gray-800">0.02ms</span></span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar space-y-4 pr-1" id="memory-facts-container">
            <!-- Dynamically rendered facts -->
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Minimalist Add Task Form Modal Overlay -->
  <div id="new-task-backdrop" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-20 hidden flex items-center justify-center z-50">
    <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-md p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-xl">
      <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Create Platform Task</h3>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 mb-1">Task Title</label>
          <input type="text" id="task-title" class="m3-input" placeholder="e.g., Deploy memory-dream-cron microservice">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 mb-1">Description / Scope Details</label>
          <textarea id="task-desc" rows="3" class="m3-textarea" placeholder="Detail specific sub-task trees..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 mb-1">Assignee</label>
            <select id="task-assignee" class="m3-select">
              <!-- Populated from TEAM_MEMBERS -->
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 mb-1">Delegation Target</label>
            <select id="task-delegation" class="m3-select">
              <option value="WORKSTREAM_AGENT">Workstream Agent</option>
              <option value="PERSONAL_AGENT">Personal Agent</option>
              <option value="HUMAN_ONLY">Human Only</option>
              <option value="HYBRID">Hybrid</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-end gap-2 mt-6">
        <button class="m3-btn-outline text-xs" onclick="closeCreateTaskModal()">Cancel</button>
        <button class="m3-btn-primary text-xs" onclick="addNewTask()">Create Task</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const envId = window.__sandboxEnvId;
    const syncKey = "ollie_control_panel_state";

    // Real Workspace Team Members
    const TEAM_MEMBERS = {
      "yadavajay@google.com": {
        name: "Ajay Yadav",
        avatar: "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5ytDzOzOxOMnVKGMTlZFIQFZGQE-F3hF9WT2C3_8rKFkSa6V4xQ=s64"
      },
      "belindapreno@google.com": {
        name: "Belinda Preno",
        avatar: "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8kkayF4FN3ib50ZpJsNFIMcSF9CLOgEcXNjlG9yhQ2xy1dL2q=s64"
      },
      "danielgiuditta@google.com": {
        name: "Daniel Giuditta",
        avatar: "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4XtQJyOGEbExqDChL5Jutn2AfMdv-Yaq9Pbdd1NMuBb-qO08=s64"
      },
      "simonsok@google.com": {
        name: "Simon Sok",
        avatar: "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJwa8yeHprZ88_pXXGVlN6TT1mDyU1T8GUcNOixdQ46wyCNDlcGA=s64"
      }
    };

    // Ollie System Microservice Definitions
    const SERVICES = [
      { id: "task", name: "Task Service", grpc: "google.workspace.ollie.v1.TaskService", description: "Authoritative state gateway for task lifecycle transitions and Spanner updates", status: "Healthy", uptime: "21d 14h", latency: 8, cpu: 1.4, throughput: 11.2 },
      { id: "fulfilment", name: "Task Fulfilment Service", grpc: "google.workspace.ollie.v1.TaskFulfilmentService", description: "Dispatches tasks and translates declarative scopes to either Sobi or Jetski harnesses", status: "Healthy", uptime: "14d 8h", latency: 12, cpu: 3.8, throughput: 4.1 },
      { id: "feed", name: "Feed Service", grpc: "google.workspace.ollie.v1.FeedService", description: "Maintains feed timelines and streams Server-Sent Events/WebSockets directly to UI", status: "Healthy", uptime: "9d 2h", latency: 5, cpu: 0.8, throughput: 16.5 },
      { id: "workstream", name: "Workstream Service", grpc: "google.workspace.ollie.v1.WorkstreamService", description: "Validates fine-grained RBAC identities and reconciles Google Group assets", status: "Healthy", uptime: "30d 1h", latency: 6, cpu: 0.5, throughput: 2.1 },
      { id: "memory", name: "Memory Service", grpc: "google.workspace.ollie.v1.MemoryService", description: "Indexes knowledge into isolated stores and runs vector similarity checks", status: "Healthy", uptime: "24d 18h", latency: 15, cpu: 2.1, throughput: 14.8 },
